    "7408502": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the Melusine",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Key, statue, key, statue, key, statue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Do you mean... that we need to put the keys in the statues? Well, that sounds about right. Three keys, three statues..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Shall we give it a try?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What happens after we place the keys?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Door opens, open door..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Door? Where? And what's behind the door?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Root, Erinnyes, very deep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "A door to the root of Erinnyes? You know so much, Pahsiv!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Pahsiv, protect!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What else do we have to know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "...Huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You know, like information! The more the merrier! The more we know, the more confident we will be!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "In...formation? In...formation... Pahsiv! Information, a lot!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Great!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Erinnyes, information, lots of."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Lots of information, uh huh."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Information, water vein, lots of."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Lots of water veins, right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Water vein, visitor, lots of."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Hmm? Visitor? Lots of? Wait, Paimon doesn't get it. Where do all these visitors come from? Or are you telling Paimon that the visitor knows how to create mirror images of themselves?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Melusine!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Water vein, visitor, taste."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Evil, visitor, sense."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Tasting the evil in the water vein? Err, what kind of flavor is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The visitor can sense information through the water veins?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Pahsiv!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Willow, collect. Fog, handle. Spring, send."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Root, water vein, center."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So, Erinnyes is the center of information?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are you saying that all of Erinnyes is the visitor's information system? And this visitor can sense something bad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "#Smart Paimon! Smart {NICKNAME}! Pahsiv!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gosh, who is this visitor named visitor?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Fontaine, visitor, protect."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "But, visitor, very busy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Purple thing, sneaking toward the root. Purple thing, secretly destroying the root."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Pahsiv, peek. Pahsiv, secretly scratch the stone tablet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So you're the one that removed the writing from the stone tablet! Was it to stop the purple thing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Pahsiv! But..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Purple thing, kept going toward the root. Purple thing, very powerful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The purple thing found another way?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Pahsiv!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Looks like this purple thing's a tough customer. If the root is destroyed, then the information system will fail to function, and the visitor's senses will be affected."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "Pahsiv, duty! Pahsiv, protect!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pahsiv",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, ka-pow. Paimon, ka-pow."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, we can't wait anymore. We need to ka-pow now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Alright then, Pahsiv! Open the door!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Excellent. Let's go!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
